00:06.000 --> 00:09.000 
It was in my third month
00:09.000 --> 00:12.000 
that the scientist took me. 
00:12.000 --> 00:14.000 
I was still a nymph
00:14.000 --> 00:16.000 
and had shed reently
00:16.000 --> 00:18.000 
my exoskeleton
00:18.000 --> 00:19.000 
lying dark and hollow 
00:19.000 --> 00:21.000 
next to my pale body.
00:21.000 --> 00:23.000 
The scientist scraped me
00:23.000 --> 00:25.000 
and some others
00:25.000 --> 00:28.000 
into a small plastic cup.
00:28.000 --> 00:31.000 
I would never see Voronezh again.
